OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA chilly start, with any early
OL,6,Flow cloud soon clearing. This will
OL,7,Fleave another fine and dry day with
OL,8,Flong sunny spells and light winds.
OL,9,FFeeling warm in the sunshine, but cool
OL,10,Fnear coasts.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA dry and sunny evening.
OL,13,FLengthy clear spells overnight will
OL,14,Fallow areas of fog to develop, with
OL,15,Ffrost likely especially in prone rural
OL,16,Fspots.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
