OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FA cold start once again, but
OL,6,Fwith early frost and fog soon clearing
OL,7,Fto leave another dry and sunny day.
OL,8,FWarmer than Thursday, but remaining
OL,9,Fcooler near coasts.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FLargely
OL,12,Fdry during this period, with some
OL,13,Fsunny spells likely. Risk of overnight
OL,14,Ffog and frost. Often cool near coasts,
OL,15,Fbut feeling warm in the sunshine,
OL,16,Fespecially inland.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
